{
  "stem": "27150.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we quickly ran to Barcelona, we got ourselves drunk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And funny thing, we were so happy, everybody, that we didn't think of the people back in Europe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, and-- because at that time the Germans surrendered in May.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at that time, we already knew unfortunately about Treblinka and about Buchenwald, about Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you see, we were sort of in mourning, you see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because everybody, you see, there were some people man and woman live together, she escaped with her husband left in Warsaw, and he escaped with a wife left in Lodz or something.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They lived together with an agreement if the husband's-- if the partner, the spouses survive, so we finish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And a few, you see, had to break up, because the spouses survived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And a few got married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And anyway, the speech ended that there is the American army ordered the Japs keep control over the town until the American Marines come over.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You see, so the next day a few officers came over by plane.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you see, Japs still had the sentries and the guards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So, and then they waited until the big ship comes with the marines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Some people were very smart.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They started to go to the Japanese district and buy a lot of merchandise.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, because they were in a big panic, and made a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A friend of mine, you see, he-- he was dealing with the Japs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was buying all the mercury quicksilver.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I said, look Henry, what-- what are you doing?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When-- when the war is over, they come and shoot you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, I don't care.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
